			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Dash:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button + D-Pad up</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Guard or confirm:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Cancel / Search / Talk / Open or close door:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Normal attack:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Confirm selected recovery item:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Switches bullet type:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Switches the status display:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Switch the homing from one target to another:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Switches the recovery items:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Switches the menu screen on/off:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Switches the map sreen on/off:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br><br>
